:Class APLGuiParameterSpace
⍝ Creates an unnamed namespace and populates it with some methods:
⍝ | `∆List` | Lists the contents of the namespace.
    ⎕IO←0 ⋄ ⎕ml←3

    ∇ n←Create
      :Access Public Shared
    ⍝ Creates an unnamed namespace and populates it with a `∆List` function.
      :Access Public Shared
      n←⎕NS'∆List' '∆MergeParms'
    ∇

    ∇ r←∆List;⎕IO
    ⍝ List all variables and possible references in this namespace.
      ⎕IO←0
      r←{⍵,[0.5]⍎¨⍵}⎕NL-2 9
    ∇

    ∇ parms←∆MergeParms parms;names
      :Access Public Shared
    ⍝ Merges parameter space ⍵ with current space; ⍵ has priority.
      :If ~0∊⍴names←' '~¨⍨↓parms.⎕NL 2 9
          parms←⎕THIS⊣parms{⍵{⍎⍺,'←⍵'}¨⍺.⍎¨⍵}names
      :EndIf
    ∇

:EndClass
